Package ohos.data.usage

Class DataUsage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.usage.DataUsage

  • public final class DataUsage
extends Object
    A basic class for device space management. This class provides interfaces to query information about external storage devices, such as their mount state and whether they are pluggable.
    Since:
    1
